  "info": {
    "name": "SB/SV Reveal QS Spoilers",
    "description": "Reveals text hidden by spoiler bars on SpaceBattles and Sufficient Velocity. \r\n\r\nSpoiler bar formatting: \r\n<code>\r\n[qs]text[/qs]\r\n</code>\r\nWithout the userstyle, text inside the spoiler bar's [qs] tags is blacked out (black text on a black background). The text is revealed when the mouse moves over the spoiler bar and the text color changes to grey. \r\n\r\nWith the userstyle installed, the color of the spoiler bar text is red so the text is always visible.",
    "additionalInfo": "2020-04-12: updated to work with XF2.",
